<F P=106> [Announcer-read report] </F>
  [Excerpt] A prime minister's motion requesting authority 
for Turkish troops to participate in a possible international 
peacekeeping force to be sent to the area for the peaceful 
solution of the conflict between Azerbaijan and Armenia has been 
submitted to the Turkish Grand National Assembly. The motion 
also asks for permission to establish certain bases on Turkish 
territory with the aim of providing logistical support to such a 
peace force. [passage omitted] 

